  <para id="Para969227">The numeric formats shown in <link
  endterm="Anchor43955" id="XRef969225" linkend="Anchor43955"> Numeric Formats
  </link>Table System.2 would apply to any fields displaying quantity,
  quantity per, Cost, currency, Price, or Extended Price information.</para>
  <note>
    <para id="Para969229">Locale fields featuring numeric values are required
    to contain a minimum of nine characters to the left of the decimal
    point.</para>
  </note>
